cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.CE, cs.SY

This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it deals with learning algorithms for MDP models. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it deals with off-policy policy evaluation in RL. Additionally, it could belong to cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) as it proposes a new finite sample generalization error bound. It could also belong to cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) as it applies the proposed approach to a HIV treatment simulation domain. Finally, it could belong to cs.SY (Systems and Control) as it deals with MDP models and policy evaluation in RL, which are relevant to control systems.
